content.body: While we'd love to have you eat in person, you can always place an order on the site by navigating to turtleheadtacos.com/orderonline. You can place an order online during your restaurant's open hours! As a reminder, you can also download our mobile app on iOS or Android for an even faster experience. Don't forget to signin so you get those rewards points. Turtle up and happy eating!
content.name: How to place a new order online
